♪Steak and a cake for a festival
meal that's yummy yum... It's time to
celebrate and fill my tummy tum...♪

I get the feeling there's a lot of
history and lore behind the winter
festival. I need to dig in and learn it all!

I'm happiest when I'm digging into a
sweet treat! I can't wait to savor the
frosting on that winter festival cake!

Winter mornings are definitely frigid,
but at least they wake you up! We
could take a little stroll to stay warm!

Let's see... To scale the chimney, we
need a ladder that's long enough to
reach when leaned at an angle, so...$k$pI'll crunch the numbers!

I'm Annette, a visitor from
$Nf's castle.$k$pI brought you a gift just to say
happy winter festival!

I'll do all I can to help make the
winter festival an absolute success!

I'm going to have to be extra sweet
to outshine this cute outfit!

Don't tell anyone, but I might have
blown up an iron pan trying to make
a winter festival Sweet Bun Trio...

You'll see! I'll make the winter festival
even more lively!

You can expect good things with
Annette Fantine Dominic lending a
hand! Count on me to help!

I'm back! All of the winter festival
gifts are in the hands of their lucky
recipients, $Nu.$k$pThis festival has taught me so much
about all sorts of things. I've been
enjoying myself the entire time!$k$pI absolutely love learning, of all kinds.
That's why I'm constantly reading up
on the latest and greatest.$k$pNow, exploring Askr and making new
friends has opened up a whole new
world of knowledge to explore!$k$pIt's been eye-opening to experience
the new things here in Askr that are
different than at home in Fodlan!$k$pI'll be sure to put everything I've
learned at the festival to good use.
You can count on it!
I bring joy!
Let's have some fun!
Sing with me!
Here, a gift!
Party's over...
Ba-dum-bump-bah!
Boom! It's done!
I'll give this festival my very best. You can count on me!
Ooh, got any more gifts to give out? I'm all done with mine.
I don't know which I'm more excited for—the presents, or the feast!
The only way to improve on tonight...would be to have my whole family here.
Oh, I almost forgot—I have something for you! Here, take it!
Ready to go!
What a dilemma...
I'm off!
